milestones.description: Hansie Cronje and McMillan's 76-run partnership is SA's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 46 between Richardson and Eric Simons
Hansie Cronje has scored 19 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for SA breaking Andrew Hudson's record
Azharuddin has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (226) for IND, going past Kapil Dev
